We're Serious About Our Core Values

Comfort

We know that feeling welcomed and comfortable is crucial to being able to open up your mind to new experiences, which is why it's so important for exploring cannabis products. Odyssey has created a warm, inviting space for you at our Hamilton weed dispensary.

Reliability

We only carry legal, regulated products that are approved safe for use by the Government of Canada. Not only that, but we only carry the best Canadian cannabis brands, so there's never a question of safety or quality when you shop at Odyssey.

Inclusivity

We believe that every person that's of legal age, regardless of their interests or previous experience with cannabis, should be able to enjoy reasonably priced weed products and accessories, in an environment free from judgement.
